dct_title_s: A general map of Saxony and Bohemia, with the adjacent countries, including all Silesia : being a specimen of a new Geographical and military atlas, to be continued occasionally
dct_description_sm: Geographic coverage complete in 40 sheets.; Relief shown pictorially.; Title from index map.; From the Gentleman's magazine, 1760.; Accompanied by index map at scale approximately 1:1,500,000. (1 map ; 22 x 36 cm.).
